title: (Mon Full) Bobby’s Birthday Recap! + Famous Bald Celeb Draft…but with a TWIST + Lunchbox Spends The Weekend with The Haunted Doll and Has A Chance To Make More Money!
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Bobby’s Birthday Recap! + Famous Bald Celeb Draft…but with a TWIST + Lunchbox Spends The Weekend with The Haunted Doll and Has A Chance To Make More Money!
description:
Bobby recaps his birthday weekend. He also addresses what he talked about on Friday that everyone thought was an April Fool’s Joke to prove it’s not! Per listener request, We draft our favorite bald celebrities but have a new TWIST for whoever comes in last. Lunchbox updates us on if anything creepy happened at his house over the weekend with the Crying Boy doll. Bobby offers him a challenge to make more money tonight.
